<div class="md:container md:mx-auto m-32 w-screen bg-gray-300 rounded-2xl">
  <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-center p-10">Contacto</h1>

  <div class="flex w-full">
    <div class="w-1/2">
      <p class="text-left text-2xl p-10 leading-10">
        Si estás buscando inspiración para tu página o deseas discutir
        requisitos específicos con nosotros, por favor, déjanos tus datos y nos
        comunicaremos contigo para brindarte la ayuda que necesitas en la
        construcción de tu sitio web.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Responsive en 1280 -->

    <div class="w-1/2 sm:w-1/1">
      <form class="w-full max-w-2xl p-10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <label
              class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2"
              for="grid-first-name"
            >
              Nombre
            </label>
            <input
              class="appearance-none block w-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded py-3 px-4 mb-3 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white"
              id="grid-first-name"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Nombre"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 px-3">
            <label
              class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2"
              for="grid-last-name"
            >
              Apellidos
            </label>
            <input
              class="appearance-none block w-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded py-3 px-4 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-gray-500"
              id="grid-last-name"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Apellidos"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-full px-3">
            <label
              class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2"
              for="grid-password"
            >
              Email corporativo
            </label>
            <input
              class="appearance-none block w-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded py-3 px-4 mb-3 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-gray-500"
              id="grid-password"
              type="email"
              placeholder="example@mail.com"
            />
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs italic"></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-3 mb-2">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <label
              class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2"
              for="grid-zip"
            >
              Número de celular
            </label>
            <input
              class="appearance-none block w-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded py-3 px-4 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-gray-500"
              id="grid-zip"
              type="text"
              placeholder="+57 300 123 4567"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <label
              class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2"
              for="grid-zip"
            >
              Nombre de la empresa
            </label>
            <input
              class="appearance-none block w-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded py-3 px-4 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-gray-500"
              id="grid-zip"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Nombre de la empresa"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 px-3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <label
              class="block uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold mb-2"
              for="grid-zip"
            >
              Ciudad
            </label>
            <input
              class="appearance-none block w-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded py-3 px-4 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-gray-500"
              id="grid-zip"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Ciudad"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-end">
          <button
            class="bg-gray-700 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded m-8 text-xl"
          >
            Enviar
          </button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
